### Table Container Component Structure (React/TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/features/data-table/GUIDE.md

Illustrates a clean component structure for a data table container. It separates data fetching and state management concerns by using custom hooks (`useUserFilters`, `useUsers`) and React Context (`DataTableProvider`). This pattern enhances maintainability and reusability.

