### Extract Filter Logic for API (React/TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/features/data-table/GUIDE.md

Shows how to extract complex filtering logic into a custom hook, `useUserFilters`, which then transforms column filters into a format suitable for API requests. This pattern promotes separation of concerns and improves code readability. It utilizes React hooks and assumes a `transformFiltersForAPI` function exists.

```tsx
const useUserFilters = () => {
  const columnFilters = useColumnFilters();
  return useMemo(() => transformFiltersForAPI(columnFilters), [columnFilters]);
};
```

